From: Esteban Urrutia <esteuwu@proton.me>
Date: Sat, 16 May 2026 21:39:21 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 03/10] dt-bindings: arm: qcom: Add ThinkPhone by motorola
 (motorola-bronco)

The ThinkPhone by motorola (motorola-bronco) is a smartphone released in 2023 featuring the SM8475 SoC.
Since this is the first device featuring this SoC, add qcom,sm8475 and qcom,sm8450 consts as well.
---
 Documentation/devicetree/bindings/arm/qcom.yaml | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/arm/qcom.yaml b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/arm/qcom.yaml
index 50cc18a6ec5e..881dc012195a 100644
--- a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/arm/qcom.yaml
+++ b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/arm/qcom.yaml
@@ -1096,6 +1096,12 @@ properties:
               - sony,pdx224
           - const: qcom,sm8450
 
+      - items:
+          - enum:
+              - motorola,bronco
+          - const: qcom,sm8475
+          - const: qcom,sm8450
+
       - items:
           - enum:
               - qcom,sm8550-hdk
-- 
